{
  "3069410": {
    "name": "Re:Fragment ~Absolute Ambition~",
    "steam_appid": 3069410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/71463ced3ad002a5991f6296d8d160f8.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/71463ced3ad002a5991f6296d8d160f8.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creators of <i>The Picture of Café au lait</i>, AstralSeal presents their third original visual novel – <i>Re:Fragment ~Absolute Ambition~</i>. In this game, there is a unique school where everyone can vote on proposals, and the ideas that receive the majority of votes become new rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/08fbe3734a7c59a402a89147a3d17f9e.poster.avif?t=1744703433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/08fbe3734a7c59a402a89147a3d17f9e.webm?t=1744703433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/08fbe3734a7c59a402a89147a3d17f9e.mp4?t=1744703433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings, 7-9 hours of story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can easily be played with one hand</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All artwork in Full HD (1080p)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intriguing mystery that unfolds itself as the story advances</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LANGUAGES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Text: English, Thai (ภาษาไทย)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice Acting: Thai - 6 Characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/97c6e459e3cf0f1768942a3056f4bf16.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/97c6e459e3cf0f1768942a3056f4bf16.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/a6c00aa32d11cf1c4a5cd3ac9e7ee832.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/a6c00aa32d11cf1c4a5cd3ac9e7ee832.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silverseal Private Academy is a pioneering model school where students have the unique opportunity to shape their school environment democratically. Decisions are made collectively by voting and those that secure a majority are enacted as policies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kusaka Yuuma, the main protagonist, is the treasurer of the student council. He works alongside his childhood friend Kuromiya Reika, the popular and respected student council president. She is a ray of sunshine that commands the attention of people wherever she goes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yuuma lives a tranquil student life, blissfully unaware of the storm brewing on the horizon. That is, until Reika unveils a new controversial policy that sparks widespread debate. Disrupting their lives and turning their world upside down, changing everything they once knew forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the story of ambitious teenagers confronted with a reality far removed from their expectations. Will they be able to navigate a life that sabotages them at every turn? It all depends on “you”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/6cdfaf51f480cb5ad5c43c60b1bb1416.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/6cdfaf51f480cb5ad5c43c60b1bb1416.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/f83e1bc23706d0a366f9576d3f3f487a.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/f83e1bc23706d0a366f9576d3f3f487a.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kuromiya Reika</strong><br>Flawless Student Council President</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character's Voice: Pugko</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silverseal Private Academy student council president. She excels at every aspect, boasting an outstanding academic performance with top grades for every subject in her year. The only subject that she can never ace is Math, where she is beaten by our protagonist Yuuma.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She is confident and treats everyone equally. This has won her the trust of not only all of the students, but the entire school faculty as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contrary to her appearance, she loves cute rabbit dolls and has never told anyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/3eadefa9aacb49eae86c8e53872bf8ee.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/3eadefa9aacb49eae86c8e53872bf8ee.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kusaka Yuno</strong><br>Avid Mobile Gacha Gamer Little Sister</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character's Voice: AidenShia </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist's little sister. She studies remotely through a homeschooling system and doesn't attend school like other kids her age due to her frail health. Because of this, she is extremely shy and anxious when meeting strangers, except for her brother.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As she is mostly confined to her home, her hobby is mainly playing gacha games. She spends a lot of money on them and has become one of the top 10 players on the server.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/16e694e832cd5650c365b1c9339f70b8.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/16e694e832cd5650c365b1c9339f70b8.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shirasaki Maya</strong><br>Kind-hearted and Trendy Girl</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character's Voice: Furorin</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An upperclassman who is friendly and gets along effortlessly with everyone. With her attractive figure and charm, she undoubtedly always becomes the center of attention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's said that many boys have confessed their love for her, but her response is always the same: “Sorry, I'm not interested in romance right now.” </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her dream is to become a fashion designer and launch her own clothing brand in the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/e1627940e018b314968492001f985f87.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/e1627940e018b314968492001f985f87.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yanagihara Risa</strong><br>Student Council Advisor + Teacher</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character's Voice: Karin Tsutsuji</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Iwano Akane</strong><br>\tDiscipline Committee Member</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character's Voice: Reilim</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kataoka Kazuma</strong><br>Student Council Vice President</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character's Voice: Ryuji</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras/4c0ee5bad88e5e0d6dcb07663ca533df.avif?t=1744703433\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069410/extras_big/4c0ee5bad88e5e0d6dcb07663ca533df.avif?t=1744703433 width=800 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Director:</strong> Rayedge<br><strong>Scenario Writer:</strong> coregameHD / Woofy<br><strong>Artist/Character Design:</strong> Rayedge / Woofy<br><strong>Programming:</strong> AstralAria</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cast:</strong><br>Reika - Pugko<br>Yuno - AidenShia<br>Maya - Furorin<br>Akane - Reilim<br>Kazuma - Ryuji<br>Risa-sensei - Karin<br>Koutarou - BaradinXDrake</p>",
